Fourth Department,

December, 1945.

(December 14, 1945.) In the Matter of Stanley G. Valenti, on Behalf of John F. Wright, as Candidate of the American Labor Party for the Public Office of Member of the Assembly, etc., Appellant, against John H. Bachman et al., as Commissioners of Election of the County of Onondaga, etc., Respondents.

Order affirmed, without costs of this appeal to any party. All concur. ■ (The order dismisses the petition.) Present — • Taylor, P. J., Dowling, Harris, McCurn and Love, JJ.
